      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. i spend 10 hours a day staring at a screen and the only people i \"interact\" with are avatars and Slack notifications. sometimes i feel like if i just stopped logging on, or if i just... wasn't here, the world wouldn't even glitch. like i'm just a ghost in the machine.",
