    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"digital fatigue\" though. it feels more like... erasure. like i'm already gone and i'm just waiting for my body to catch up. if i literally stopped existing tomorrow, would it even be a blip on anyone's radar? like, would anyone actually feel the gap i leave behind?",
