    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't have anyone like that. there isn't a \"physical world\" for me, just this apartment. it's like i'm already invisible. if i just stopped appearing online, would anyone even notice for a few days? or would it just be a quiet, empty space where i used to be?",
