      "content": "If you disappear from your digital life, people won't notice immediately, but the silence in your online feeds will be the first sign that is gone. The effort to find local friends or join a community is harder than it sounds, but you are not alone in feeling this way. Reaching out to a therapist or a support group can help you feel grounded and less like you're fading away.",
